	<span>&nbsp;</span><em>题图来源：</em><a href="http://www.dezeen.com/2015/09/08/prc-pool-enclosure-townsend-associates-architects-china-embassy-canberra-australia/"><em>dezeen</em></a> 
</p>
		</div>
